Package: panelbuild
Title: Post-Import Panel Data Auditing and Preparation Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Lavanya", "Desiraju", email = "desirajulavanya@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: panelbuild provides tools for auditing, validating, and preparing longitudinal and panel datasets prior to statistical analysis. The package detects duplicate unit-time observations, identifies missing panel cells, summarizes panel balance, flags data-quality issues, and creates reproducible panel-completion workflows without altering observed data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
